Quickstrike:






Quickstrike suddenly spun around, hearing two voices that were not familiar 
to him. His eyes went wide and jolted as he saw Marine and Pheniox that the 
threshold of the door. Didn't he ever get a break?

He thrusted his cobra arm out and fired at the two of them. He then half 
limped and half leaped over to the side, hoping to escape any throwbacks 
from the two other Predacons.
